### 2.4 استبدال `GET /users/{id}/roles` — GetWithRoles بـ GetUserRoles
- [x] **حذف** Action `GetWithRoles` كاملاً (`GetWithRolesAsync` محذوفة من IUserService)
- [x] **حذف** Action `GetUserRoles` القديم (int id)
- [x] إضافة action جديد:
  ```csharp
  [HttpGet("{id}/roles")]
  [Authorize(Roles = "Admin")]
  [ProducesResponseType(typeof(ServiceResponse<IEnumerable<string>>), 200)]
  public async Task<IActionResult> GetUserRoles(string id)
  {
      var response = await _userService.GetUserRolesAsync(id);
      return Ok(response);
  }
  ```

